In 1971, a bureau of forced testing of cars was created in the Office of the Chief Designer of the enterprise. The experience gained in competitions helped to better prepare equipment, which was reflected in the subsequent successful performances of the plant's autosportsmen, in particular, the performance of the VAZ-Autoexport team at " Tour of Europe - 73 "[121]. In the 1970s-1980s, the Autoexport team on specially prepared VAZ cars of various models participated in various circuit races and rallies in Europe. Ladas actively participated in a wide variety of auto competitions held in the USSR , and now continue to participate in tournaments, not only in Russia, but also in other post-Soviet countries. Jacques Pok cherished the dream of Niva's participation in major international automotive competitions aniah.